He bursted(burst) with laughter and said that
he didn't know, that he just wanted to practice.

55
00:03:30,739 --> 00:03:33,099
I said, okey we'll start tomorrow.

56
00:03:33,098 --> 00:03:37,348
So he came over and I noticed that he bought
